<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="ko">
<head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8">
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
    <title>온라인 매출전표</title>
    <!-- 기존 Noto Sans 폰트 (주석 처리됨) -->
    <!-- <link href="https://fonts.googleapis.com/css2?family=Noto+Sans:wght@400;700&display=swap" rel="stylesheet"> -->

    <!-- Pretendard 폰트 적용 -->
    <link rel="stylesheet" href="https://cdn.jsdelivr.net/gh/orioncactus/pretendard/dist/web/variable/pretendardvariable.css">

    <style>
        body {
            /* Pretendard 폰트 적용 */
            font-family: 'Pretendard Variable', sans-serif;
            background-color: #f4f4f4;
            display: flex;
            justify-content: center;
            align-items: center;
            margin: 0;
            padding: 20px;
            min-height: 100vh;
        }

        .receipt-container {
            background: white;
            width: 100%;
            max-width: 320px; /* 아이폰 SE 기준 폭 */
            border: 1px solid #ccc;
            border-radius: 8px;
            padding: 10px;
            box-shadow: 0 4px 10px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.2);
        }

        .receipt-header {
            display: flex;
            justify-content: space-between;
            align-items: center;
            background: #0078d7;
            color: white;
            padding: 10px;
            border-radius: 6px 6px 0 0;
            position: relative;
        }

        .receipt-header .logo {
            font-weight: bold;
        }

        .receipt-header .title {
            font-size: 16px;
            font-weight: bold;
            flex: 1;
            text-align: center;
        }

        .close-btn {
            position: absolute;
            top: 50%;
            right: 10px;
            transform: translateY(-50%);
            background: #f44336;
            color: white;
            border: none;
            border-radius: 50%;
            width: 24px;
            height: 24px;
            font-size: 16px;
            cursor: pointer;
            line-height: 24px;
            text-align: center;
        }

        .receipt-section {
            margin-top: 10px;
            padding: 10px;
            border: 1px solid #ccc;
            border-radius: 4px;
        }

        .section-title {
            font-size: 14px;
            font-weight: bold;
            margin-bottom: 10px;
            color: #333;
        }

        .info-table {
            width: 100%;
            border-collapse: collapse;
            font-size: 12px;
        }

        .info-table th, .info-table td {
            padding: 6px;
            text-align: left;
        }

        .info-table th {
            background: #f9f9f9;
            color: #333;
            font-weight: bold;
        }

        /* 강조된 섹션 스타일 */
        .highlight-row {
            background: #e8f4fc;
            border-radius: 4px;
            padding: 10px;
        }

        .highlight-row th, .highlight-row td {
            font-weight: bold;
            color: #0078d7;
        }

        .footer {
            background: #0078d7;
            color: white;
            text-align: center;
            margin-top: 10px;
            border-radius: 4px;
            padding: 10px;
            font-size: 12px;
        }

        .footer a {
            color: #ffeb3b;
            text-decoration: none;
            font-weight: bold;
        }

        .footer a:hover {
            text-decoration: underline;
        }

        .footer-small {
            background: #f9f9f9;
            color: #555;
            text-align: center;
            margin-top: 5px;
            padding: 10px;
            font-size: 10px;
            border: 1px solid #ddd;
            border-radius: 4px;
        }

        /* 반응형 디자인 */
        @media (max-width: 320px) {
            .receipt-container {
                max-width: 100%;
                border-radius: 0;
                box-shadow: none;
            }

            .receipt-header .title {
                font-size: 14px;
            }

            .info-table th, .info-table td {
                font-size: 10px;
                padding: 5px;
            }

            .footer {
                font-size: 10px;
                padding: 8px;
            }

            .footer-small {
                font-size: 9px;
                padding: 5px;
            }
        }
    </style>
</head>
<body>
    <div class="receipt-container">
        <!-- Header -->
        <div class="receipt-header">
            <div class="logo">로고</div>
            <div class="title">온라인 매출전표</div>
            <button class="close-btn" onclick="closeReceipt()">×</button>
        </div>

        <!-- Section 1: 결제정보 -->
        <div class="receipt-section">
            <div class="section-title">결제정보</div>
            <table class="info-table">
                <tr>
                    <th>결제방법 (방식)</th>
                    <td>신용카드 / 체크카드</td>
                </tr>
                <tr>
                    <th>카드종류</th>
                    <td>비씨카드</td>
                </tr>
                <tr>
                    <th>카드번호</th>
                    <td>1321-1213-10312</td>
                </tr>
                <tr>
                    <th>할부개월</th>
                    <td>일시불 / 12개월</td>
                </tr>
                <tr>
                    <th>거래유형</th>
                    <td>승인 / 취소</td>
                </tr>
                <tr>
                    <th>승인번호</th>
                    <td>132131231</td>
                </tr>
                <tr>
                    <th>결제금액</th>
                    <td>44,000</td>
                </tr>
                <tr>
                    <th>공급가</th>
                    <td>40,000</td>
                </tr>
                <tr>
                    <th>부가세</th>
                    <td>4,000</td>
                </tr>
            </table>
        </div>

        <!-- Section 2: 구매정보 -->
        <div class="receipt-section">
            <div class="section-title">구매정보</div>
            <table class="info-table">
                <tr>
                    <th>거래일시</th>
                    <td>2024-12-12 17:10</td>
                </tr>
                <tr>
                    <th>상품명</th>
                    <td>신속개발강의</td>
                </tr>
                <tr>
                    <th>구매자명</th>
                    <td>이민자</td>
                </tr>
                <tr>
                    <th>주문번호</th>
                    <td>1232321</td>
                </tr>
            </table>

            <!-- 강조된 섹션 -->
            <div class="highlight-row">
                <table class="info-table">
                    <tr>
                        <th>사업장명</th>
                        <td>초특급개발센터</td>
                    </tr>
                    <tr>
                        <th>대표자명</th>
                        <td>일론머스크</td>
                    </tr>
                    <tr>
                        <th>사업자등록번호</th>
                        <td>124-00-12345</td>
                    </tr>
                    <tr>
                        <th>사업장주소</th>
                        <td>경기도 가평군 복길 직로 999</td>
                    </tr>
                    <tr>
                        <th>상점문의</th>
                        <td>1669-2255</td>
                    </tr>
                </table>
            </div>
        </div>

        <!-- Footer 1 -->
        <div class="footer">
            신용카드 청구서에는 <a href="https://inicis.com" target="_blank">이지플랫전자결제(주)</a>로 표시됩니다.<br>
            This Transaction will be billed by EGFP Inc.
        </div>

        <!-- Footer 2 -->
        <div class="footer-small">
            부가세법 시행령 제57조 2항에 따라 결제대행업체를 통한 신용카드 매출전표를 발행한 경우에는 사업자가 별도의 세금계산서를 교부할 수 없습니다.
        </div>
    </div>

    <script>
        function closeReceipt() {
            document.querySelector('.receipt-container').style.display = 'none';
        }
    </script>
</body>
</html>
